{
  "stem": "1775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 118.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The Jewish Judenrat find places for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Some people just take-- took in families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was one of them that took in a, a family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they lived with me all the time until they went away to the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The-- in-- the, the first few-- let's say in the '39, '40, '41, it was not so bad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was bad, but not so bad because there, there wasn't massive killing like later-- like it started later.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Once the war broke out between the Russians and the Germans, that's when our-- really, everything started to blow up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They just started to get more vicious and terrible.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They used to get ahold of somebody and kill him just for nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They always killed people for nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I, I don't know if you call it fortunate or not fortunate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I got a permit to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I was  working for the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We used to go out-- sometimes they used to keep us for the whole week and take us back to the city for the weekend.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And sometimes, we went-- in different places I worked, we just had to come in the morning to work, and in the evening we went back to our homes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that was until 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Of-- like two weeks before Rosh Hashanah of 1942, real hell broke loose in Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It was the first action.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they took, at that time, I think about more than 10,000 people away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "The Germans didn't even expect to take so many people, that they didn't realize that so many people would listen to them, I guess, and come on that Marktplatz.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But we thought we were going to be resettled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Just like they were resettling the other people, that they going to resettle us.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
